Bublup gives you the power to stay on top of your work projects and personal passions. The Bublup Chrome extension helps you get more done and feel in control of your life. Save and visually organize anything you find on the web.

Extension Features:
* Instantly save any web page, article, video, and more to your Bublup folders.
* Launch the Bublup web app to access all of your folders.
